@startuml
title Healthcare Portal - User Interaction States

[*] --> Idle

state Idle
state Registration
state Login
state FacilitiesAccess
state NewsAccess
state SymptomCheck
state FitnessCheck
state ServiceCompletion
state InsuranceValidation
state PaymentProcess
state CashPayment
state InsurancePayment
state FeedbackCollection
state Logout

Idle : entry / Display Welcome

Idle --> Registration : New User / Start Registration
Registration --> Login : Registration Completed / Login
Login --> FacilitiesAccess : User Signed In / Access Facilities
Login --> NewsAccess : User Signed In / Read News
Login --> SymptomCheck : User Signed In / Check Symptoms
Login --> FitnessCheck : User Signed In / Use Fitness Check
FacilitiesAccess --> Login : Sign In / Access Facilities
NewsAccess --> Login : Sign In / Read News
SymptomCheck --> Login : Sign In / Check Symptoms
FitnessCheck --> Login : Sign In / Use Fitness Check
ServiceCompletion --> Login : Sign In / Continue Using
ServiceCompletion --> FeedbackCollection : Service Completed / Collect Feedback
FeedbackCollection --> Logout : Finish Session / Log Out
InsuranceValidation --> PaymentProcess : Validate Insurance / Process Payment
PaymentProcess --> InsurancePayment : Insurance Payment Chosen / Complete Payment
PaymentProcess --> CashPayment : Cash Payment Chosen / Collect Details
CashPayment --> InsurancePayment : Insurance Payment Chosen / Complete Payment
InsurancePayment --> FeedbackCollection : Payment Completed / Collect Feedback
Logout --> Idle : Log Out / End Session

@enduml
